title: Is there anything more frustrating than seeing your team do horribly stupid things?
body:
I got autofilled support. I ain't even mad. My naut support is pretty clean for my elo. 

It just tears me apart inside when I do the best I can but my teammates are being overtly terrible at everything they are doing though... Like we all have bad games... but ffs don't back as an adc with 1600 gold and come back to lane with tier 2 boots, 2 pots and 1 longsword...

It feels like a sick game sometimes... when you get autofilled and you do your best but everything goes to shit in the first 10 minutes.
